{"tid":807044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「范冰冰案件」牽扯到香港富商","createTime":"2018-09-05T08:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T18:13:30.000Z","uid":134071,"like":83,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"ff29ccaa089d609c42e6c1f622fcf9684df42b89","tid":807044,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:05:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2541418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2541418&d=A6FaUYi8mbmnD2E3fogqrZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=bc54b089\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2541418&h=fa5fe113\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2541418</a><br />\n<br />\n逃稅醜聞擺不平！范冰冰風暴再擴大 爆牽涉台港富商<br />\n2018/09/05 08:25 <br />\n<br />\n〔記者曾德蓉／台北報導〕中國女星范冰冰涉入逃稅醜聞， 自從被爆與經紀人穆曉光遭到逮捕後，已離奇消失2個月，因此出現各種都市傳說，之前一度冒出范冰冰安全下莊，直奔美國尋求政治庇護的說法，不過目前依然沒有任何人士出面證實；現在又有最新報導指稱，范冰冰案情牽涉到台灣、港澳及中國富商與官員，短期內恐怕無法落幕。<br />\n<br />\n據中媒報導，范冰冰赴美尋求政治庇護的消息已被否認，但研判背後團隊可能確實曾試圖運作，當局才會刻意傳出消息，包括監控起居、限制出境等，現在已證實此路不通；<strong>此外，范冰冰逃稅事件背後牽涉到橫跨台灣、港澳及中國的富商與官員，風暴隨時可能擴大。</strong>"},{"pid":"cab6b2d6a7685709bb5af1919dcee8c5f56dc88f","tid":807044,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:06:29.000Z","msg":"邊位香港官員應該會難估d? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265263f177ec17e45c651bb239b8f09a8dcf02ef","tid":807044,"uid":158270,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"cab6b2d6a7685709bb5af1919dcee8c5f56dc88f","tid":807044,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:06:29.000Z","msg":"邊位香港官員應該會難估d? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:10:55.000Z","msg":"我估陳帆"},{"pid":"738954c46626a01605d90de9196a811a36de52a3","tid":807044,"uid":190383,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:12:03.000Z","msg":"Hello無圖